page.title: 09Greenwich
page.content: Greenich has lots of tourists visiting every year.The main tourist attractions are the Cutty Sark,the Royal Naval College,the Gipsy Moth and the Maritime Museum.The Cutty Sark is a tea clipper.Its figurehead is a witch holding a horses tail.Inside the hold there is a collection of other figureheads. Greenwich is also well known for the Meridian Line which runs through Greenwich park.In the park is the Maritime Museum and Queen Annes house the ceilings of which has paintings of heavenly people.In the park there are also swings a boating lake and some tennis courts.
